ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
PrecisAuthorization for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to (a) enter into a contract with The Standard Life Assurance Company in order to provide its employees and their dependents with basic life insurance, optional life insurance and long-term disability insurance and (b) pay its portion of the premiums.
